# Extended 5-Face Dashboard Implementation

I have completed the extension of the SignalSource website to include the 5-face dashboard, fulfilling all requirements while maintaining the existing Landing Page and Medical Audit functionality.

## Changes Implemented

### 1. Navigation & Routing Structure
- **React Router Integration**: Replaced the initial static render in [main.tsx](file:///Users/joshkie/Library/CloudStorage/Dropbox/SignalSource/src/main.tsx) with a fully functional `RouterProvider`.
- **Landing Page Kept Intact**: The main website remains at `/`. The existing CTA buttons now route to the new `/dashboard` experience.
- **New Dashboard Layout**: Created [Dashboard.tsx](file:///Users/joshkie/Library/CloudStorage/Dropbox/SignalSource/src/app/pages/Dashboard.tsx) featuring a glassmorphism sticky top navigation bar with the 5 required tabs.

### 2. The 5 Dashboard Faces
- **Medical Audit**: Preserved the original simulator and dashboard preview.
- **Evidence Pack**: Textarea-based form for Encounter IDs with compliance checklist results.
- **Risk Radar**: CSV-driven risk analysis with a dynamic moderate/high risk score and recommended actions.
- **Creator Feed**: Multi-platform analytics dashboard with automated action plans for content growth.
- **Opportunity Scanner**: Industry-specific grant scanner with business profile filtering.

### 3. Universal Polling Pattern
Implemented a reusable [usePolling](file:///Users/joshkie/Library/CloudStorage/Dropbox/SignalSource/src/app/lib/usePolling.ts#6-80) hook ([src/app/lib/usePolling.ts](file:///Users/joshkie/Library/CloudStorage/Dropbox/SignalSource/src/app/lib/usePolling.ts)):
- Sends the initial `POST` with `X-Tenant-ID: demo-tenant`.
- Polls the `GET` endpoint every 2 seconds for status updates.
- Manages loading/error/data states consistently across all new pages.

